39
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:02,880
By the way,

40
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,480
what is A Cha doing now?

41
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,520
She's

42
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,680
busy having Mr. Liu
taste-test her dishes.

43
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:14,800
Dayuan.

44
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,840
Go get me a squad of soldiers.

45
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,000
