46
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:05,680
Mr. Liu! Mr. Liu!

47
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,760
Coming!

48
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,560
Wait a minute.

49
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,600
I'll be right there!

50
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,240
Right away.

51
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,480
I'm coming!

52
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,360
Mr. Liu,

53
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,240
uncouth men like us

54
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,480
