every day at the border.

55
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:21,040
You've got to take good care
of our skin.

56
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,640
Rest assured. You can count on it.

57
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,040
Mr. Liu.

58
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:27,120
Coming! Bro, I'll be right back!

59
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,080
Wait for me, one second.

60
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,840
You said it'd take a quarter hour

61
00:04:33,840 --> 00:04:34,760
before taking this off?

62
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:35,920
Almost half an hour now. Peel it off!

63
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,120
I'm sorry!

64
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,920
Mr. Liu.

65
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,000
Coming!

66
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,320
Mr. Liu.

67
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:40,840
Mr. Liu.

68
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,200
Sorry, I'll be back right away.

69
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,600
Mr. Liu, hurry up!

70
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,760
I came earlier.

71
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:47,760
Why not my turn yet?

72
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,760
I'm so sorry!

73
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:49,760
A good massage for you.

74
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,000
My back is hurting.

75
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,040
Mr. Liu.

76
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:56,560
- Mr. Liu.
- Mr. Liu.

77
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,280
I'll be right there.

78
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,840
Can I take off the facial, Mr. Liu?

79
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,600
Hurry up!

80
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:03,760
Right away.

81
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,720
I want a facial mask, Mr. Liu.

82
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,520
Coming!

83
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,120
Don't worry. I am coming!

84
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,040
Be gentle.

85
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:15,600
Wait a minute.

86
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:24,720
Today, the daughter of the Lord
of Vermilion Bird City,

87
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,120
Princess Gongsun comes to visit.

88
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,720
I heard she is your niece.

89
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:34,880
