97
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:01,000
Yes, exceedingly wonderful.

98
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,200
Very good.

99
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,400
(You think of hitting on her,)

100
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,920
(but you don't know if she would agree.)

101
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,680
Move aside.

102
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,560
Princess Gongsun.

103
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,040
Second Young Master.

104
